  <section id="studio_village" class="img_w_txt">
    <div class="txt_box">
      <h2>Klubben</h2>
      <p>
        A stunning event space with a high ceiling and walkway, perfect for
        weddings, parties, confirmations, corporate events, and kick-offs.
        You’re welcome to bring your own food and drinks, and the atmosphere
        speaks for itself.
      </p>
      <p>
        The venue includes a lit outdoor lounge terrace with parasols,
        professional sound and lighting, cooling for your own beverages,
        dishwasher access for glassware, and final cleaning.
      </p>
      <p>
        Located on the ground floor with direct access, the space is approx. 100
        m² and can host up to 50 seated or 80 standing guests. Check-in is from
        12:00 on the day of the event, and check-out is by 12:00 the following
        day.
      </p>

