        <ul>
          <li>Rental: 8,500 DKK</li>
          <li>Deposit: 5,000 DKK</li>
          <li>Cleaning (included)</li>
          <li>Optional walk-away cleanup: 1,500 DKK</li>
          <li>Table/chair rental (up to 60 guests): 2,000 DKK</li>
          <li>Catering kitchen with fridge, freezer & dishwasher: 3,000 DKK</li>
