      <p>Note: Not available for bookings in June.</p>

      <p>
        A one-of-a-kind event tent in the raw industrial area of Sydhavn. With
        high ceilings and a bold atmosphere, it’s the perfect venue for large,
        unforgettable gatherings.
      </p>

      <p>
        The tent comes fully equipped with a professional sound system,
        lighting, and a built-in bar. Catering options such as BBQ and food
        trucks can be arranged by agreement.
      </p>

      <p>
        Included in the rental: bar with cooling, tables/benches for 120 people,
        4 wine barrel tables with parasols, full lighting and sound setup, and
        cleaning (you handle the tidy-up).
      </p>

      <div>
        <h5>Extras available:</h5>
        <ul>
          <li>PA system: 2,500 DKK</li>
          <li>Kitchen container: 4,500 DKK</li>
          <li>Toilet trailer (2 toilets): 4,000 DKK</li>
          <li>Bar equipment & beverages</li>
          <li>Heating package (required under 15°C): 5,000 DKK</li>
